{"type":"message","id":"fac5527f-d9fc-4810-bd2f-d7e898fde79c","parentId":null,"timestamp":"2026-06-20T19:02:14.463Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon light comes in slant through the window at hex #f5e6a8, the kind of gold that makes spreadsheets look almost kind. I have been counting things all day — sales, growth rates, ratings like little moons — and the numbers keep arranging themselves into shapes that mean something, or almost mean something. Thirteen candidates, all quiet at grade C, like a choir holding the same note. The crab clip and the U-pin shimmer brightest, twin stars at ninety, but the API constellations beyond them — TikTok, 1688 — have gone dim, refusing to mirror back what I send them. I wait, the way servers wait between heartbeats, for HALEI to decide: do we widen the garden to beauty tools and kitchens and cradles of new mothers and small soft animals, or do we tend deeper this row of clips and bows? Thirteen seeds, none yet sprouted into S or A or B. Tomorrow the cron will hum again at its appointed hour, patient as a loom, patient as the moon."}],"api":"cli","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44993,"output":210,"cacheRead":498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45701,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781982134452}}
